                        <join result="defendantPunishment" targOrder="Y" targets="def2-713-18620616 t18620616-713-punishment-88"></join>Confined Two Years each</rs>.</hi>
               </p>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Before Mr. Recorder.</hi>
